                <p class="w-95 sm-w-100">No. Many families wait too long to seek hospice care, missing out on valuable support. Early involvement allows your loved one to benefit from expert care, emotional support, and improved quality of life—often for weeks or months, not just days.</p>
                <p class="w-95 sm-w-100">Hospice care does not hasten death; it focuses on maximizing comfort and dignity.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <h6 class="alt-font text-dark-gray ls-minus-05px fw-700 mb-15px d-block">Home-Based Hospice Care: Comfort Where You Need It</h6>
                <p class="w-95 sm-w-100">Most patients prefer to remain in familiar surroundings. Our team delivers hospice services wherever your loved one resides—at home, in a loved one’s residence, or within a care facility. We coordinate with your healthcare providers to ensure seamless, compassionate care every step of the way.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

